snippet.title: Vertebreaker Technical Preview
snippet.description:
For Friday the 13th, here's a first look at the new Vertebreaker!

Vertebreaker is a comically-"spooky" action platformer that is still in early development

The technical preview will be available for Windows on September 27th so everyone can get a feel for what's ahead!

Stick with us until this Halloween, when we'll launch a full gameplay demo and a Kickstarter to bring the game to completion!

Check out Headcannon on the web!
http://www.headcannon.com

Join the discussion on Discord!
https://t.co/26dgTfBWti
